      "article_html": "<article><p><span class=\"sent\" data-sentence=\"To anyone I’ve offended, I just want to say, I reinvented electric cars and I’m sending people to Mars in a rocket ship.\"><span class=\"w\">To</span> <span class=\"w\">anyone</span> <span class=\"w\">I</span>’ve <span class=\"w\">offended</span>, <span class=\"w\">I</span> <span class=\"w\">just</span> <span class=\"w\">want</span> <span class=\"w\">to</span> <span class=\"w\">say</span>, <span class=\"w\">I</span> <mark class=\"vocab\" data-cat=\"vocab\" data-word=\"reinvented\" data-lemma=\"reinvent\" data-freq=\"rare\" data-level=\"beyond\" data-idx=\"0\">reinvented</mark> <span class=\"w\">electric</span> <span class=\"w\">cars</span> <span class=\"w\">and</span> <span class=\"w\">I</span>’m <span class=\"w\">sending</span> <span class=\"w\">people</span> <span class=\"w\">to</span> <span class=\"w\">Mars</span> <span class=\"w\">in</span> <span class=\"w\">a</span> <span class=\"w\">rocket</span> <span class=\"w\">ship</span>. </span> <span class=\"sent\" data-sentence=\"Did you think I was also going to be a chill, normal dude?\"><span class=\"w\">Did</span> <span class=\"w\">you</span> <span class=\"w\">think</span> <span class=\"w\">I</span> <span class=\"w\">was</span> <span class=\"w\">also</span> <span class=\"w\">going</span> <span class=\"w\">to</span> <span class=\"w\">be</span> <span class=\"w\">a</span> <span class=\"w\">chill</span>, <span class=\"w\">normal</span> <span class=\"w\">dude</span>?</span></p><p><span class=\"sent\" data-sentence=\"—Elon Musk, Saturday Night Live , May 8, 2021\">—<span class=\"w\">Elon</span> <span class=\"w\">Musk</span>, <span class=\"w\">Saturday</span> <span class=\"w\">Night</span> <span class=\"w\">Live</span> , <span class=\"w\">May</span> 8, 2021</span></p><p><span class=\"sent\" data-sentence=\"The people who are crazy enough to think they can change the world are the ones who do.\"><span class=\"w\">The</span> <span class=\"w\">people</span> <span class=\"w\">who</span> <span class=\"w\">are</span> <span class=\"w\">crazy</span> <span class=\"w\">enough</span> <span class=\"w\">to</span> <span class=\"w\">think</span> <span class=\"w\">they</span> <span class=\"w\">can</span> <span class=\"w\">change</span> <span class=\"w\">the</span> <span class=\"w\">world</span> <span class=\"w\">are</span> <span class=\"w\">the</span> <span class=\"w\">ones</span> <span class=\"w\">who</span> <span class=\"w\">do</span>.</span></p><p><span class=\"sent\" data-sentence=\"—Steve Jobs\">—<span class=\"w\">Steve</span> <span class=\"w\">Jobs</span></span></p></article>",
